    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616114",
        "quote": "Perhaps this is one of the last remaining strands of my Catholic upbringing, but to me the word 'worship' means absolute unquestioning affirmation of the authority of the deity. I'll not have that in my life. If you are wise, neither will you.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Brendan Myers",
            "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616114"
        },
        "topics": [
