    {
        "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616109",
        "quote": "Call it a case of observer bias on my part, but Humanist Paganism seems to be an emerging option for those who want to be part of the Pagan community, but who want to be a little more intellectual about their practices, and they really don't care about the 'woo' anymore.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Brendan Myers",
            "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616109"
