            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616124",
        "quote": "I earned my Ph.D. in philosophy, and one of my specializations was the logic and mathematics of game theory. I've also got a degree in drama, so I know about stories, characterizations, plot arcs, and the like. Lots of game designers can do one or the other: I've got the skills for both.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Brendan Myers",
            "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616124"
