            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/brendan_myers_616125",
        "quote": "I've invented several games for use as teaching tools in my classroom: one of them, a game called 'Iron Age: Council of the Clans,' got so popular among my students that they encouraged me to publish it, which I did.",
